OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,FWords by Lucy L. Middleton
OL,8,FInfluencers in Dubai who post images
OL,9,Fand video online of "incident sites or
OL,10,Fdamage" caused by missiles will face
OL,11,Flegal action "without leniency", the
OL,12,FUAE's Attorney-General has warned.
OL,14,FThe UAE has detected 205 ballistic
OL,15,Fmissiles since Iran began retaliatory
OL,16,Fstrikes against Israel and the US, of
OL,17,Fwhich 190 were destroyed, the
OL,18,Fcountry's ministry of defence said.
OL,26,@sD@NOUsD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,FThe strikes have brought Dubai into
OL,7,Fthe spotlight online, as residents of
OL,8,Fthe city - considered by many to be a
OL,9,Fsafe haven in the Middle East - posted
OL,10,Fvideos of missiles in the sky during
OL,11,Fthe first days of the conflict.
OL,13,FDamage has been reported at Dubai
OL,14,FInternational Airport and several
OL,15,Fluxury hotels in the city.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,FAt the same time, a viral trend has
OL,7,Femerged on platforms like Instagram
OL,8,Fand TikTok, in which images of the
OL,9,FEmir of Dubai Sheikh Mohammed bin
OL,10,FRashid Al Maktoum, and the prime
OL,11,Fminister, are being used to express
OL,12,Fhow safe the city is.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,FOn Friday, the Attorney-General warned
OL,7,Fagainst even resharing other people's
OL,8,Fcontent "documenting incident sites or
OL,9,Fdamage resulting from the fall of
OL,10,Fprojectiles or shrapnel in some areas"
OL,11,Fof the UAE.
OL,13,F"Publishing such materials, or
OL,14,Fcirculating inaccurate information
OL,15,Fabout them may incite panic among
OL,16,Fcommunity members and create a false
OL,17,Fimpression of the true situation in
OL,18,Fthe country," warned the statement,
OL,19,Fposted via the UAE's Public
OL,20,FProsecution account on X.
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,FThe statement said "publishing or
OL,7,Fcirculating these clips or misleading
OL,8,Finformation" would constitute
OL,9,F"behaviour contrary to the law" if it
OL,10,Fresults in "spreading fake news, or
OL,11,Fharming public security and order".
OL,13,FThe UAE is home to stringent
OL,14,Fcybercrime laws, which impose strict
OL,15,Fpenalties for digital offences, such
OL,16,Fas spreading false information or
OL,17,Frumours, invading someone's privacy,
OL,18,For accessing someone's computer
OL,19,Fsystem, without permission.
OL,26,@qD@_O]rD@LOUsD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,FThese can be punishable by prison
OL,7,Ftime, fines of up to $77,000 (around
OL,8,F#57,600), or travel bans.
OL,10,FThe wording of the law is "so vague
OL,11,Fand grey", almost anyone with a social
OL,12,Fmedia account is at risk of breaking
OL,13,Fit, Detained in Dubai Chief Executive
OL,14,FRadha Stirling told ITV News.
OL,16,F"You can't post anything negative, or
OL,17,Fconsidered to be misinformation, which
OL,18,Fis determined by the government, so
OL,19,Fthat could be your genuine opinion or
OL,20,Fan opinion held by many people,"
OL,21,FStirling said.
OL,26,@rD@[OUsD@IO]xD@AOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,F"Whether they call it national
OL,7,Fsecurity, national interest, at the
OL,8,Fend of the day they have a strong
OL,9,Fvested interest in maintaining the
OL,10,Fimage that Dubai is safe, that this is
OL,11,Fa temporary issue, and that they have
OL,12,Fbeen fully able to defend the country."
OL,14,FStirling said she had received
OL,15,Fmultiple phone calls from British
OL,16,Fcitizens looking for a way out of the
OL,17,Fcity, some of whom are on travel bans
OL,18,Fpreventing them from leaving the
OL,19,Fcountry.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,FTravel bans are often worse than a
OL,7,Ffine or prison sentence because they
OL,8,Fcan take years to resolve, Stirling
OL,9,Fsaid. They can be issued for reasons
OL,10,Flike cybercrime violations, civil
OL,11,Fdisputes or debt.
OL,13,F"I think it would be naive to assume
OL,14,Fthings are safe right now anywhere in
OL,15,Fthe Middle East, even in Cyprus and
OL,16,FTurkey," Stirling said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@XxtxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,F"The reality is you've got people
OL,7,Flined up on mattresses sleeping in car
OL,8,Fparks, you've got children screaming
OL,9,Fand crying and people desperately
OL,10,Ftrying to get in touch with their
OL,11,Fembassies."
OL,13,FViral videos attesting to safety of
OL,14,Fthe UAE frequently pose the question
OL,15,Fon-screen: "You live in Dubai, aren't
OL,16,Fyou scared?", followed by the same
OL,17,Fimages of UAE leaders, with the
OL,18,Fresponse: "No, because I know who
OL,19,Fprotects us."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@KO]wD@LOUxD@LO]zD@KOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,FThe clips are accompanied by an AI-
OL,7,Fgenerated cover of "Papaoutai (Afro
OL,8,FSoul)". The lyrics translate to: "Tell
OL,9,Fme, where is your dad? Without even
OL,10,Fhaving to speak to him, he knows
OL,11,Fwhat's wrong."
OL,13,FInfluencer and sports coach Anastasiya
OL,14,FMakshayeva, 27, moved to Dubai three
OL,15,Fyears ago after falling in love with
OL,16,Fthe city when she visited her friend.
OL,17,FShe has posted multiple videos
OL,18,Fhighlighting the safety of Dubai since
OL,19,Fthe war broke out, including her own
OL,20,Fversion of the trend.
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@FO]pD@bOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,F"Initially, I posted simply to
OL,7,Freassure my followers, family and
OL,8,Ffriends who were worried about me and
OL,9,Fconstantly asking about the situation
OL,10,Fin Dubai. I wanted to show that I
OL,11,Fbelieve life here will remain calm and
OL,12,Fstable," Makshayeva, who is half
OL,13,FRussian and Ukrainian, told ITV News.
OL,15,FMakshayeva said life was continuing as
OL,16,Fnormal in the city, and she
OL,17,Funderstands and respects the rules
OL,18,Fregarding responsible behaviour online.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31012
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,F"It's very important not to spread
OL,7,Fmisleading information or create
OL,8,Fpanic," she said.
OL,10,F"Most people around me are not
OL,11,Finvolved in politics - we came here
OL,12,Fand live here because we value safety,
OL,13,Fstability and the opportunity to build
OL,14,Four lives peacefully."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@GO]rD@AOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31013
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,FRhea Jacobs, a model and entrepreneur
OL,7,Fwho has lived in Dubai since
OL,8,Fchildhood, said the last few days had
OL,9,Freinforced for her how safe the city
OL,10,Fis, particularly when compared to
OL,11,Fcountries experiencing the reality of
OL,12,Fwar, like Gaza, Sudan and Syria.
OL,14,F"I think for many people in the West
OL,15,Fit can sometimes be confusing to see
OL,16,Fresidents of UAE openly expressing
OL,17,Fsupport and appreciation for the
OL,18,Fcountry, its government, and its
OL,19,Fleadership," Jacobs said.
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31014
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772885581
OL,3,CDubai residents say city is safe as
OL,4,CUAE warns against posting online
OL,6,F"Some may assume that people are being
OL,7,Fasked or pressured to post in that
OL,8,Fway, but that is far from the truth.
OL,9,FFor many of us, this support comes
OL,10,Ffrom genuine gratitude."
OL,12,FJacobs said she thought the Attorney-
OL,13,FGeneral's warning applied to
OL,14,F"exaggerated, sensationalised, or
OL,15,Fedited videos" being posted for "views
OL,16,Fand clickbait", such as an AI-
OL,17,Fgenerated clip of the Burj Khalifa on
OL,18,Ffire.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@XO]vD@AOUwD@NO]wD@aOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
